    <note>Zhang(2) Jie(3) [345] His ancestors were all Yuzhang jun Zhang(2). Pin's [342] grandson. His father, Fang [3184], moved to Wuxian and established the northern branch of the Wuxian Zhang(2) lineage (zu). Liang's [7159] father, Jie(2)'s [334] and Bo's [343] grandfather, Dexiang's [344] collateral kin, Liu(2) Kui's [8092] father-in-law. He(2) Bifei [7235] was the father-in-law of Jie(3)'s son, Zai [3189]. Zai's daughters were all wives of literati (shiqi). XCB, 254.17a, 259.1a, 260.4a, 306.4a, 376.4a, 425.21b, 442,.2b, 480.10a, 482.8b; SS, 328.30b; Suzhou FZ, 77.15b ff.; Sun Di, Daquanji, 56.7b; YLDD, 12506.10a; Fujian TZ, 147.23a has him as a Pucheng jinshi in 1065. CBD, 3, 2079-80.</note>
